invariant concurrent_futures_extra139.broken_executor_base_name_len_12:
  description: "concurrent.futures.BrokenExecutor.__bases__[0].__name__.__len__() == 12 — concurrent.futures.BrokenExecutor.__bases__[0].__name__ is 'RuntimeError' (12 chars); BrokenExecutor inherits directly from RuntimeError rather than Exception, reflecting the severity of a broken executor; BrokenExecutor.__name__=='BrokenExecutor' (len=14); BrokenExecutor.__doc__.__len__()==74; NEW in extra139: first standalone BrokenExecutor base class name length invariant; verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11"
